title: Plane of Truth
tooltip: universal property: creatures cannot deliberately lie here
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature can't tell a deliberate lie. It can avoid answering questions, or be evasive in its answers, as long as it remains within the boundaries of the truth.